{"tha-ap396:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap396:0.2":"Pilindavacchavagga ","tha-ap396:0.3":"Madhudayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap396:1.1":"“Sindhuya nadiya tire, ","tha-ap396:1.2":"sukato assamo mama; ","tha-ap396:1.3":"Tattha vacemaham sisse, ","tha-ap396:1.4":"itihasam salakkhanam. ","tha-ap396:2.1":"Dhammakama vinita te, ","tha-ap396:2.2":"sotukama susasanam; ","tha-ap396:2.3":"Chalange paramippatta, ","tha-ap396:2.4":"sindhukule vasanti te. ","tha-ap396:3.1":"Uppatagamane ceva, ","tha-ap396:3.2":"lakkhanesu ca kovida; ","tha-ap396:3.3":"Uttamattham gavesanta, ","tha-ap396:3.4":"vasanti vipine tada. ","tha-ap396:4.1":"Sumedho nama sambuddho, ","tha-ap396:4.2":"loke uppajji tavade; ","tha-ap396:4.3":"Amhakam anukampanto, ","tha-ap396:4.4":"upagacchi vinayako. ","tha-ap396:5.1":"Upagatam mahaviram, ","tha-ap396:5.2":"sumedham lokanayakam; ","tha-ap396:5.3":"Tinasantharakam katva, ","tha-ap396:5.4":"lokajetthassadasaham. ","tha-ap396:6.1":"Vipinato madhum gayha, ","tha-ap396:6.2":"buddhasetthassadasaham; ","tha-ap396:6.3":"Sambuddho paribhunjitva, ","tha-ap396:6.4":"idam vacanamabravi. ","tha-ap396:7.1":"‘Yo tam adasi madhum me, ","tha-ap396:7.2":"pasanno sehi panibhi; ","tha-ap396:7.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap396:7.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap396:8.1":"Imina madhudanena, ","tha-ap396:8.2":"tinasantharakena ca; ","tha-ap396:8.3":"Timsa kappasahassani, ","tha-ap396:8.4":"devaloke ramissati. ","tha-ap396:9.1":"Timsa kappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap396:9.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap396:9.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap396:9.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap396:10.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayado, ","tha-ap396:10.2":"oraso dhammanimmito; ","tha-ap396:10.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap396:10.4":"nibbayissatinasavo’. ","tha-ap396:11.1":"Devaloka idhagantva, ","tha-ap396:11.2":"matukucchim upagate; ","tha-ap396:11.3":"Madhuvassam pavassittha, ","tha-ap396:11.4":"chadayam madhuna mahim. ","tha-ap396:12.1":"Mayi nikkhantamattamhi, ","tha-ap396:12.2":"kucchiya ca suduttara; ","tha-ap396:12.3":"Tatrapi madhuvassam me, ","tha-ap396:12.4":"vassate niccakalikam. ","tha-ap396:13.1":"Agara abhinikkhamma, ","tha-ap396:13.2":"pabbajim anagariyam; ","tha-ap396:13.3":"Labhi annassa panassa, ","tha-ap396:13.4":"madhudanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap396:14.1":"Sabbakamasamiddhoham, ","tha-ap396:14.2":"bhavitva devamanuse; ","tha-ap396:14.3":"Teneva madhudanena, ","tha-ap396:14.4":"pattomhi asavakkhayam. ","tha-ap396:15.1":"Vutthamhi deve caturangule tine, ","tha-ap396:15.2":"Sampupphite dharaniruhe sanchanne; ","tha-ap396:15.3":"Sunne ghare mandaparukkhamulake, ","tha-ap396:15.4":"Vasami niccam sukhito anasavo. ","tha-ap396:16.1":"Majjhe mahante hine ca, ","tha-ap396:16.2":"bhave sabbe atikkamim; ","tha-ap396:16.3":"Ajja me asava khina, ","tha-ap396:16.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo. ","tha-ap396:17.1":"Timsakappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap396:17.2":"yam danamadadim tada; ","tha-ap396:17.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap396:17.4":"madhudanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap396:18.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap396:18.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap396:18.3":"Sabbasava parikkhina, ","tha-ap396:18.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo. ","tha-ap396:19.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap396:19.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap396:19.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap396:20.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap396:20.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap396:20.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap396:21.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma madhudayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap396:22.1":"Madhudayakattherassapadanam catuttham. "}